{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875884934,"sessionID":"ses_2858d638affemr61pumzKHgw4C","part":{"id":"prt_d7a731701001807tna4T50wgov","messageID":"msg_d7a72f7fa001MBdKPcVIBay5E3","sessionID":"ses_2858d638affemr61pumzKHgw4C","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_59f9cee7ccf04a76a5c6db11","state":{"status":"error","input":{"content":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Module: root | Language: Makefile | Size: M | Design: [Stage ST-3 completed]\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### T1. 基础构建目标 (Basic Build Targets)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** 定义全局变量: `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `GO_VERSION`, `BINARY_VERSION`\n- [ ] **T1.2** 实现 `docker-build` 聚合目标，调用 router/workload-manager/agentd 子目标\n- [ ] **T1.3** 实现 `docker-build-router` 目标，构建 router 镜像\n- [ ] **T1.4** 实现 `docker-build-workload-manager` 目标，构建 workload-manager 镜像\n- [ ] **T1.5** 实现 `docker-build-agentd` 目标，包含 picod\n- [ ] **T1.6** 添加并行构建支持 (使用 `MAKEFLAGS += --jobs` 或 `.NOTPARALLEL` 控制)\n- [ ] **T1.7** 实现 `docker-build-all` 作为 `docker-build` 的别名\n\n### T2. 镜像推送目标 (Docker Push Targets)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** 实现 `docker-push` 聚合目标\n- [ ] **T2.2** 实现 `docker-push-router` 目标\n- [ ] **T2.3** 实现 `docker-push-workload-manager` 目标\n- [ ] **T2.4** 实现 `docker-push-agentd` 目标\n- [ ] **T2.5** 添加 `docker-buildx-push` 系列目标用于多平台构建 (参考 CI/CD design.md)\n- [ ] **T2.6** 支持通过环境变量覆盖镜像仓库 (`IMAGE_REGISTRY`)\n\n### T3. 验证目标 (Validation Targets)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** 实现 `validate-dockerfiles` 目标，验证所有 Dockerfile 语法\n- [ ] **T3.2** 实现 `validate-images` 目标，验证镜像内二进制可执行\n- [ ] **T3.3** 添加镜像标签一致性验证\n- [ ] **T3.4** 添加构建产物哈希校验目标 (可选)\n\n### T4. 清理目标 (Cleanup Targets)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** 实现 `docker-clean` 目标，清理本地构建镜像\n- [ ] **T4.2** 添加 `docker-prune` 目标，清理 dangling 镜像\n- [ ] **T4.3** 添加 `clean-all` 目标，清理所有构建产物\n\n### T5. 测试目标 (Test Targets)\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** 实现 `test` 目标，运行 Go 单元测试\n- [ ] **T5.2** 实现 `test-cover` 目标，带覆盖率报告\n- [ ] **T5.3** 实现 `e2e` 目标，调用 E2E 测试脚本\n- [ ] **T5.4** 实现 `e2e-clean` 目标，清理 E2E 测试环境\n- [ ] **T5.5** 添加 `test-all` 聚合目标 (unit + e2e)\n\n### T6. 代码质量目标 (Lint & Code Quality)\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** 实现 `lint` 目标，运行 golangci-lint\n- [ ] **T6.2** 实现 `lint-fix` 目标，自动修复 lint 问题\n- [ ] **T6.3** 实现 `gen-check` 目标，验证代码生成是否最新\n- [ ] **T6.4** 实现 `gen-copyright` 目标，生成版权头\n- [ ] **T6.5** 添加 Python lint 目标 (`lint-python`, 使用 ruff)\n\n### T7. 辅助目标 (Helper Targets)\n\n- [ ] **T7.1** 添加 `.PHONY` 声明所有伪目标\n- [ ] **T7.2** 实现 `help` 目标，显示所有可用目标及说明\n- [ ] **T7.3** 添加默认目标 `all` (默认执行 `docker-build`)\n- [ ] **T7.4** 实现版本信息目标: `version` 打印当前版本变量\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- T1.1 → T1.2-T1.7\n- T2.1 → T2.2-T2.4\n- T3.1, T3.2 → T3.3 (可选)\n- T5.1 → T5.2\n- T5.2, T5.3 → T5.5\n\n## Verification Criteria\n\nEach task is independently verifiable by running:\n- `make <target>` to execute the target\n- `make help` to list all available targets\n- `make -n <target>` for dry-run validation","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md"},"error":"You must read file /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md before overwriting it. Use the Read tool first","time":{"start":1775875884923,"end":1775875884931}}}}
